# --- PERMITIR (Whitelist) ---

# Carpetas (necesario permitir la carpeta para entrar en ella)
!scripts/
!aso-app-codigo-fuente/
!Antigravity/
!backend/
!frontend/
!skills/
!skills-library/
!vault/
